      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON DREAMS (8) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (23.12) at Gawler in a Special conditions race. Can make amends this time. CATCH MY DESIGN (4) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from six tries. Was out of the placings last time (20.32) at this track in a TG1-4W, finishing fourth and beaten 7 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. ADHANA LULU (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (23.54) at Mt Gambier. Form here sound including three wins. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to feature. LIFE'S A JOKE (1) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
